kpi.name: M8019C0

kpi_info.title: Number of NACC from LTE to GSM attempts per neighbor cell relationship
kpi_info.use: This measurement provides the number of NACC from LTE to GSM attempts per neighbor cell relationship. UPDATED: Transmission of the RRC:MobilityFromEUTRANCommand message (with cell change order to GSM; 3GPP TS 36.331) from the serving eNB to the UE indicates the attempt of a Network Assisted Cell Change (NACC) from LTE to GSM.

kpi.kpi_alias: Number of NACC from LTE to GSM attempts per neighbor cell relationship
